### 2. List all files in the project
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/files/list
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. List files filtered by Contentful entry ID
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/files/list?uriMask={{contentful_entry_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get file status for a specific file
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/file/status?fileUri={{file_uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get file status for a specific file
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/locales/{{locale_id}}/file/status?fileUri={{file_uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get file status with locale information
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/file/status?fileUri={{file_uri}}&includeAuthorizedLocales=true
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get detailed file information
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/file?fileUri={{file_uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. List files with specific file types
GET {{base_url}}/files-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}/files/list?fileTypes=json,xml,properties
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Get project locales
GET {{base_url}}/projects-api/v2/projects/{{project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
